front.title: Proton Bombs
front.gametext: Deploy on a bomber: When present during a Force drain, may target a related interior site. Draw destiny. Site 'collapsed' if destiny > 4. OR May fire in a Bombing Run battle. Draw destiny. All characters, starships and vehicles with that destiny number at same site are lost.
front.lore: Proton-scattering energy warheads. Especially effective against rayand energy-shielded targets. Ineffective against particle deflector.
